<H3> <TI>   * Cultural Assistant Appointment Announced </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  94LA0091A Tehran KEYHAN-E HAVA'I in Persian 9 Feb 94 p 4 </F>
<F P=103> 94LA0091A </F>
<F P=104>  Tehran KEYHAN-E HAVA'I </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Persian </F>
Article Type:CSO 

  [Text] By order of Engineer Seyyed Mohammad Beheshti, 
executive director of the Farabi Foundation, Mr. Ja'far Jelveh 
was appointed as this foundation's cultural assistant and 
assumed his duties. Since the beginning of the Islamic 
revolution he has been manager of the Radio Drama Group. 

</TEXT>

