<H3> <TI>   * New University Appointments Announced </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  94LA0093B Tehran SALAM in Persian 2 Feb 94 p 3 </F>
<F P=103> 94LA0093B </F>
<F P=104>  Tehran SALAM </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Persian </F>
Article Type:CSO 

  [Text] The Tehran University public relations office 
reports that by order of Dr. Gholam'ali Afruz, president of 
Tehran University, Hojjat ol-Eslam val-Moslemin Baha'ol-Din 
Qahramaninezhad-Sa'eq was appointed supervisor of Tehran 
University's Koran Studies Institute. 

</TEXT>

