<F P=100> Egypt </F>
<H3> <TI>   Parties Condemn Hebron Incident, Issue Statements </TI></H3>
<H4>   Wafd Party Issues Statement </H4>
<F P=102> NC0203161194 Cairo AL-WAFD in Arabic 28 Feb 94 p 1 </F>
<F P=103> NC0203161194 </F>
<F P=104>  Cairo AL-WAFD </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Arabic </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [Statement issued by the Wafd Party on the al-Ibrahimi </F>
Mosque massacre--date not given] 
  [Text] Muslim society and the international community in 
general are heartbroken at the report of the massacre 
perpetrated by a fanatical Zionist inside the al-Ibrahimi Mosque 
in which dozens of Palestinians were martyred and hundreds 
others were injured, unarmed victims who were praying to God 
from their hearts during the dawn prayers. 
  This massacre is to be added to the crimes that the 
Palestinian people have been subjected to since the Dayr Yasin 
massacre, which was perpetrated by criminal thugs whose 
objective was to uproot the Palestinian people from their lands 
and possessions and to give these lands and possessions to 
tyrants and despots. And these despots went ahead with the 
judaization of the Palestinian land in accordance with a vile 
scheme that resulted in covering the Palestinian territories 
with settlements and colonies that are like a spearhead in the 
Arab nation's body. 
  The al-Ibrahimi Mosque massacre constitutes a crime against 
all humanity. It is the black fruit of the tendencies of hatred 
and bigotry that Zionism is planting in the hearts of its 
followers, thus prompting them to kill and practice violence and 
urging them to annihilate the Arabs so that the land will be 
theirs alone and Israel's area can expand to include the entire 
Middle East, with sovereignty over and control of all the 
peoples of the region. 
  The treacherous bullets that assassinated the worshippers in 
the al-Ibrahimi Mosque wounded the hearts of the Arabs, Muslims 
and supporters of right and justice everywhere. These bullets 
have undermined the peace hopes of everyone. Israel's rulers are 
secretly hatching plots while talking publicly about peace. They 
are the ones who gave the terrorrist an opportunity to attack 
the worshippers and it is they who cover up for the criminals 
after each massacre. 
  The Wafd Party, which firmly believes that justice must win 
and injustice is bound to be vanquished sooner or later, 
believes that this ugly crime must open the eyes of the Arab 
rulers to the extent of the Israeli danger. The Arab rulers 
must rise above differences, conflicts, and hatreds and stand 
united against the schemes being hatched against us so as to 
turn us into lackies of the Israeli state under the slogan of 
the Middle East policy. The Arab peoples should be aware of the 
danger coming from Israel and those who stand behind Israel. 
The Wafd Party, while feeling the enormity of the catastrophe 
inflicted on the Palestinian people in the occupied territories, 
is confident that this catastrophe will make this heroic people 
more determined, stronger, and more steadfast. The martyrs who 
were slain by the bullets of treachery are in an Assembly of 
Truth, in the Presence of a Sovereign Omnipotent, in the company 
of prophets (who teach), the sincere (lovers of truth), the 
witnesses (who testify), and the righteous (who do good): Ah! 
what a beautiful fellowship. [Koranic verse] 
  [Signed] Muhammad Fu'ad Siraj-al-Din 
  Wafd Party leader. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

