<F P=102> NC0203210594 Cairo MENA in Arabic 2045 GMT 2 Mar 94 </F>
<F P=103> NC0203210594 </F>
<F P=104>  Cairo MENA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Arabic </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Cairo, 2 Mar (MENA)--A huge peaceful march was 
staged in Cairo this evening by thousands of youths and women. 
The participants condemned the Israeli actions in the occupied 
territories and the bestial massacre of innocent Palestinians in 
the al-Ibrahimi Mosque in Hebron. Thousands of worshippers came 
out of the 'Amr-Ibn-al-'Ass Mosque after evening prayers and 
joined the march, which proceeded to the al-Rawdah and al-Manyal 
areas chanting slogans and carrying placards condemning that 
abominable crime. Police vehicles escorted the peaceful march to 
protect it. 

