<H3> <TI>   Court To Issue Judgment </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  NC0403070194 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el in Hebrew 0500 GMT 4 Mar 
94 </F>

<F P=103> NC0403070194 </F>
<F P=104>  Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Hebrew </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Bezeq Company employees in the Haifa district and 
the north returned to work last night but telephone disruptions 
elsewhere in the country continue. The Bezeq Company did not 
order employees to return to work last night and conducted 
negotiations with them to secure their agreement to end the 
disruptions. Our correspondent Meron Tzur reports that the 
employees have not said whether they will end disruptions before 
the District Labor Court issues a judgment on Sunday. 

</TEXT>

