Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> ["Message of gratitude" to President Borhanoddin Rabbani </F>
from Iranian President 'Ali Akbar Hashemi-Rafsanjani; date not 
given] 
  [Text] I received with great pleasure your excellency's 
message of congratulation on the occasion of the anniversary of 
the Islamic Revolution of Iran. We laid the foundation of the 
new Islamic regime on the basis of the strong faith of our 
nation and on the leadership of Grand Ayatollah Imam 
Khomeyni--the blessing of God be upon him--as well as on 
