<H3> <TI>   Rocket Attack Reportedly Carried Out in Kashmir </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  BK0203153894 Islamabad PTV Television Network in English 
1400 GMT 2 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> BK0203153894 </F>
<F P=104>  Islamabad PTV Television Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] In occupied Kashmir, mojahedin carried out a rocket 
attack on Brigade Headquarters at Kashmir Ghati in Punch area, 
causing heavy losses to the Indian forces. Reports say 
mojahedin also attacked military targets in various localities 
of Srinagar. Two Indian soldiers were killed in a grenade attack 
in Bata Kadal. 
  Meanwhile, another 16 Kashmiris were martyred in clashes and 
due to indiscriminate firing by Indian troops. A shootout 
between mojahedin and the Indian troops was reported from Wirk 
in Doda area. Mojahedin claimed that a number of Indian troops 
were killed and wounded in the clash. 

</TEXT>

