<F P=100> Palestinian Affairs </F>
<H3> <TI>   Hamas Warns Settlers To Leave Before 15 Mar </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  JN0703131594 Paris Radio Monte Carlo in Arabic 1210 GMT 7 
Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> JN0703131594 </F>
<F P=104>  Paris Radio Monte Carlo </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Arabic </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] The 'Izz al-Din al-Qassam Battalions, the military 
wing of the Islamic Resistance Movement, Hamas today addressed a 
final warning to Jewish settlers to leave their settlements. In 
a statement distributed in the occupied territories, it set 15 
March as the deadline for this evacuation. 
  The statement, which is signed by the command of 'Izz al-Din 
al-Qassam Battalions, says that it has decided to reply 
militarily through five stages, and that each stage will make 
the Israeli people and settlers weep over their dead. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

