<H3> <TI>   Officials Discuss Developments in Church Bombing </TI></H3>
<H4>   Fadlallah Comments </H4>
<F P=102> NC0403183794 Beirut Voice of Lebanon in Arabic 1715 GMT 4 
Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> NC0403183794 </F>
<F P=104>  Beirut Voice of Lebanon </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Arabic </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] 'Allamah Muhammad Husayn Fadlallah has demanded 
that the perpetrators of the Zuq Mikha'il church massacre be 
tracked down because this crime is not a Christian or Muslim 
problem. It is a Lebanese-Arab problem. Fadlallah believes 
that this is a crucial stage and that the situation in the 
region will be moving toward further mix up. He affirmed that 
any shake-up in the Arab reality will have echoes in Lebanon. 

</TEXT>

