<F P=100> JORDAN </F>
<H3> <TI>   Five Arrested in Connection With Explosions </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  JN0803111194 Amman AL-BILAD in Arabic 9 Mar 94 p 1 </F>
<F P=103> JN0803111194 </F>
<F P=104>  Amman AL-BILAD </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Arabic </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] The security organs have recently carried out a 
limited search campaign in the village of Abu-Nusayr and 
al-Baq'ah camp and arrested five persons on suspicion of 
connection with recent explosions and Jordanian Afghans. One of 
those arrested is called 'Ali Ahmad 'Iqab. 

</TEXT>

